25:56.255 --> 25:57.486
Only seven known cases

25:57.487 --> 25:58.715
in medical history.

25:58.716 --> 26:00.656
You, young lady,

26:00.657 --> 26:02.594
one in a billion.

26:02.595 --> 26:04.095
Wow. Lucky me.

26:04.096 --> 26:05.723
Well, you are lucky

26:05.724 --> 26:07.348
because we can remove it.

26:07.349 --> 26:09.226
Not today, because the tumor is

26:09.227 --> 26:11.102
right up beside your thyroid.

26:11.103 --> 26:12.646
So we have to use chemotherapy

26:12.647 --> 26:14.188
to shrink the tumor down

26:14.189 --> 26:15.357
to a size where we

26:15.358 --> 26:16.524
can get around it.

26:16.525 --> 26:18.151
In the meantime, you

26:18.152 --> 26:19.776
need this tracheostomy

26:19.777 --> 26:21.447
